    "instructions_for_student": "Drag each object tile from the left panel into the 'I observe' column of the table. Then type or select the material(s) it is made of in the right column. Objects with multiple materials — like a pen (plastic + metal + ink) or a school bag (cloth + metal) — can have more than one material chip. Use the orange suggestion buttons as hints. Fill all 15 rows to complete the activity!",
